eng.title: The Speech banana is the yellow area where most speech sounds, like "la-la-la" or "ba-ba-ba," are heard.
eng.speaker: MUTE/UNMUTE

swe.title: Speech banana är det gula området där de flesta tal ljud, som "la-la-la" eller "ba-ba-ba," hörs.

fin.title: Puhebanaani on keltainen alue, jossa useimmat puheäänet, kuten "la-la-la" tai "ba-ba-ba," kuuluvat.
